# Santa API Documentation

## Base URL
```
https://santa.test/api
```

---

## Authentication
Most endpoints require Bearer token authentication in the `Authorization` header:
```
Authorization: Bearer {token}
```

Token can be obtained from the `/telegram/start` endpoint.

---

## Public Endpoints (No Auth Required)

### 1. Register User / Login
**Endpoint:** `POST /telegram/start`

**Description:** Registers or updates a Telegram user and returns authentication token.

**Required Fields:**
- `telegram_id` (string, max: 64) - Unique Telegram user ID
- `username` (nullable, string, max: 255)
- `first_name` (nullable, string, max: 255)
- `last_name` (nullable, string, max: 255)
- `is_premium` (nullable, boolean)
- `photo_url` (nullable, URL format)
- `language_code` (nullable, string, max: 16)

**Example Request:**
```json
{
  "telegram_id": "1218682559",
  "username": "kingkong",
  "first_name": "King",
  "last_name": "Kong",
  "is_premium": false,
  "photo_url": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "language_code": "en"
}
```

**Example Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User registered successfully",
  "user": {
    "id": 1,
    "telegram_id": "1218682559",
    "username": "kingkong",
    "first_name": "King",
    "last_name": "Kong",
    "is_premium": false,
    "language_code": "en",
    "photo_url": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
    "role": "user",
    "is_admin": false,
    "created_at": "2026-04-11T05:04:31Z"
  },
  "auth_token": "153|7Y77V4MUhXWHbPjS7srUuBeN6ncGRnODYQciu6ak38b60dab",
  "token_type": "Bearer"
}
```

