## Testing with cURL

### Register/Login
```bash
curl -X POST "https://santa.test/api/telegram/start" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "telegram_id": "1218682559",
    "username": "kingkong",
    "first_name": "King",
    "last_name": "Kong"
  }'
```

### Add to Cart (with token)
```bash
curl -X POST "https://santa.test/api/telegram/cart" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "product_id": 80,
    "qty": 1
  }'
```

### Get Cart
```bash
curl -X GET "https://santa.test/api/telegram/cart" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"
```

